Natural minor scales follow a WholeHalfWWHWW - step pattern
Major scales follow a WholeWholeHalfWWWH - step pattern
The relative minor of a key is also the 6th step in the major scale
Melodic minor has a flat 6 and 7 going up, and natural 7 and 6 going down
Harmonic minor is a natural minor with a raised 7
